- Update Status.LastSyncStartTime. Go to Syncing state
- In Syncing state
- Create or Update manual trigger ReplicationDestination for each PVC
- Wait all RDs in the group are successfully to receive the date from source
by checking the manual string in spec and status
- Get LatestImage from each RD and update Status.LatestImages in the ReplicationGroupDestination
- Update Status.LastSyncStartTime to nil, and Status.SetLastSyncTime. Go to Cleanup state
- In Cleanup state
- Update Status.LastSyncStartTime to now to go to Syncing state
